<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٣٤٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4511">عَلِيُّ بْنُ الْجَعْدِ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5529">مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ جُحَادَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2511">أَبِي حَازِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a>: <span class="c2">«نَهَى النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَنْ كَسْبِ الْإِمَاءِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>